# Mini Message Board

A simple message board application built with Node.js and Express.

Live Demo: https://mini-message-board-nlk6.onrender.com

Features:

- View a list of messages
- Submit new messages
- Server-side routing with Express
- Templating using EJS
- Custom 404 and 500 error pages
- Environment variable configuration for production deployment

Tech Stack:

- Node.js
- Express
- EJS
- CSS
- Render (Deployment)

Installation & Setup:

1. Clone the repository: git clone git@github.com:Anuj-Kumar0/Mini-Message-Board.git
2. Navigate into the project: cd mini-message-board
3. Install dependencies: npm Install
4. Create a `.env` file: PORT = 3000
5. Start the server: node app.js
6. Visit: http://localhost:3000


